    Battleship
    A class to contain all information on the complete Battleship.

    Contains the information on a single section of the battleship.
    BattleshipRunner
    This class runs the the classic game of Battleship.
    BattleshipWorld
    A class to extend ActorWorld to work with the Battleship game.
    Computer
    Sets up computer's battleship locations and sets how to pick ships on their turn
    Game
    Handles how the game runs.
    MainMenu
    A basic menu to setup the Battleship game.
    ScoreMenu
    Creates a menu to update the score of the players as the game progresses
